### ================================================================
### Java 模型配置管理测试 (:8082)
### ================================================================

### 1. 查询配置列表（apiKey 脱敏）
GET http://localhost:8082/api/model-configs

### 2. 新增模型配置
POST http://localhost:8082/api/model-configs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "provider": "deepseek",
  "baseUrl": "https://api.deepseek.com",
  "modelName": "deepseek-chat",
  "apiKey": "sk-your-deepseek-key",
  "scenario": "chat"
}

### 3. 修改配置
PUT http://localhost:8082/api/model-configs/{{config_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "provider": "deepseek",
  "baseUrl": "https://api.deepseek.com",
  "modelName": "deepseek-chat",
  "apiKey": "sk-your-deepseek-key",
  "scenario": "chat"
}

### 4. 设为默认
POST http://localhost:8082/api/model-configs/{{config_id}}/default

### 5. 删除配置
DELETE http://localhost:8082/api/model-configs/{{config_id}}

### ================================================================
### Python 内部接口
### ================================================================

### 6. 获取默认配置（apiKey 解密明文）
GET http://localhost:8082/internal/model-configs/default?userId=1&scenario=chat


### ================================================================
### Python qa-agent 测试 (:8000)
### ================================================================

### 1. 创建会话
POST http://localhost:8000/api/conversations
Content-Type: application/json

{"title": "测试会话"}

### 2. 会话列表
GET http://localhost:8000/api/conversations?page=1&size=10

### 3. 会话详情（含消息）
GET http://localhost:8000/api/conversations/{{conversation_id}}/messages?page=1&size=50

### 4. 修改会话标题
PATCH http://localhost:8000/api/conversations/{{conversation_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{"title": "新标题"}

### 5. 流式对话 SSE
POST http://localhost:8000/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{"conversation_id": {{conversation_id}}, "question": "什么是技术监督？", "user_id": 1}

### 6. 非流式测试（不持久化）
POST http://localhost:8000/api/chat/test
Content-Type: application/json

{"question": "你好", "user_id": 1}

### 7. 删除会话
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/conversations/{{conversation_id}}

